sequenceDiagram
    participant pg_cron
    participant ProcessEnrichmentQueue
    participant OpenAI_LLM
    participant ImageAPI
    participant SupabaseStorage
    participant SpeciesTable

    pg_cron->>ProcessEnrichmentQueue: Fire every 5 minutes
    ProcessEnrichmentQueue->>SpeciesTable: SELECT FROM species WHERE icon_url IS NULL LIMIT 1
    SpeciesTable-->>ProcessEnrichmentQueue: Unenriched species row

    Note over ProcessEnrichmentQueue: Phase 1 - Classify
    ProcessEnrichmentQueue->>OpenAI_LLM: Classify species
    OpenAI_LLM-->>ProcessEnrichmentQueue: animal_class, climate, size, brawn/wit/speed, food_preference
    ProcessEnrichmentQueue->>SpeciesTable: UPDATE species SET classification fields, enrichver_classify = PIPELINE_VERSION

    Note over ProcessEnrichmentQueue: Phase 2 - Icon Prompt
    ProcessEnrichmentQueue->>OpenAI_LLM: Generate icon prompt
    OpenAI_LLM-->>ProcessEnrichmentQueue: icon_prompt text
    ProcessEnrichmentQueue->>SpeciesTable: UPDATE species SET icon_prompt, enrichver_icon_prompt

    Note over ProcessEnrichmentQueue: Phase 3 - Art Prompt
    ProcessEnrichmentQueue->>OpenAI_LLM: Generate art prompt
    OpenAI_LLM-->>ProcessEnrichmentQueue: art_prompt text
    ProcessEnrichmentQueue->>SpeciesTable: UPDATE species SET art_prompt, enrichver_art_prompt

    Note over ProcessEnrichmentQueue: Phase 4 - Generate Icon
    ProcessEnrichmentQueue->>ImageAPI: Generate 128x128 PNG from icon_prompt
    ImageAPI-->>ProcessEnrichmentQueue: Icon image data
    ProcessEnrichmentQueue->>SupabaseStorage: Upload icon PNG
    SupabaseStorage-->>ProcessEnrichmentQueue: Public URL
    ProcessEnrichmentQueue->>SpeciesTable: UPDATE species SET icon_url, enrichver_icon

    Note over ProcessEnrichmentQueue: Phase 5 - Generate Art
    ProcessEnrichmentQueue->>ImageAPI: Generate 512x512 PNG from art_prompt
    ImageAPI-->>ProcessEnrichmentQueue: Art image data
    ProcessEnrichmentQueue->>SupabaseStorage: Upload art PNG
    SupabaseStorage-->>ProcessEnrichmentQueue: Public URL
    ProcessEnrichmentQueue->>SpeciesTable: UPDATE species SET art_url, enrichver_art

    Note over ProcessEnrichmentQueue,SpeciesTable: Species is now FULLY ENRICHED.<br/>Each phase can fail independently.<br/>enrichver stamps track which pipeline version produced each field.
